comment: Morrow (OKC) makes incidental contact with Rozier (BOS) after he retrieves the rebound.
Olynyk (BOS) maintains legal guarding position on the driving shot attempt by Westbrook (OKC).
Christon (OKC) makes marginal contact with Bradley (BOS) away from the play.
Christon (OKC) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Smart (BOS) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court (Boston ball) was upheld.
Horford (BOS) sets the screen on Morrow (OKC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Adams (OKC) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Horford (BOS) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Adams (OKC) sets the screen on Bradley (BOS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Adams (OKC) and Horford (BOS) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Westbrook (OKC) makes contact with the ball off of Bradley's (BOS) knee and causes it to go into the backcourt. Any player may recover a loose ball after loss of team control.
Bradley (BOS) and Westbrook (OKC) have both hands firmly on the ball and a held ball is called.
Roberson (OKC) maintains legal guarding position as he contests Smart's (BOS) shot attempt.
Rozier (BOS) commits a take foul on Westbrook (OKC)
